love is a feature complete bug free strongly typed programming language

the only valid program in the language is love

the love program contains the text "love", optional newline for convenience and nothing else

if translations of the language and spec are provided, they will be included in optional branches if verified

you are encouraged to fork love, but the only correct and bug free version known is the one provided here

love is free to use and distribute, and is rumored to be good for your health

only a person who deserves pain worse than death would say "love is weaker than hate"
